-- EUROPE RESEARCH ROUNDUP- Roche, BASF, Intesa Sanpaolo 
-- 
-- Thu Dec 04, 2014 02:33AM EST
-- None



Dec 4 (Reuters) - Securities analysts revised their ratings and price targets on several European companies, including Glaxosmithkline and Arcelormittal, on Thursday.

HIGHLIGHTS * Pharmaceuticals: Jefferies lifts price targets on Roche <ROG.VX>, others [ID:nWNAB05F5R] * Italian Banks: Jefferies starts coverage of Unicredit <CRDI.MI>, Intesa Sanpaolo <ISP.MI>Following is a summary of research actions on European companies reported by Reuters on Thursday. Stock entries are in alphabetical order.* Arcelormittal <ISPA.AS>: Barclays ups target to 13.70 eur from 13.50 eur;rating overweight * Astrazeneca <AZN.L>: Jefferies raises target price to 5500p; rating buy * BASF <BASFn.DE>: Barclays cuts target price to 91 euros from 92 euros; rating overweight * Bayer AG <BAYGn.DE>: Jefferies raises target price to 140 euros; rating buy * Braas Monier <BMSA.DE>: Jefferies starts with buy; price target euros 19.20 * Glaxosmithkline <GSK.L>: Jefferies raises target price to 1400p; rating hold * ICAP <IAP.L>: Barclays raises target price to 465p from 435p; rating overweight * Intesa Sanpaolo <ISP.MI>: Jefferies starts with buy rating; 3 euros target price * Novartis AG <NOVN.VX>: Jefferies raises price target to Sfr 110; rating buy * Novo Nordisk <NOVOb.CO>: Jefferies raises price target to Dkk 300; rating hold * Roche <ROG.VX>: Jefferies raises price target to Sfr 335; rating buy * Sanofi <SASY.PA>: Jefferies raises price target to 81 euros; rating hold * Sports Direct <SPD.L>: Jefferies cuts price target to 880p from 1000p; rating buy * Unicredit <CRDI.MI>: Jefferies starts with hold rating; 5.50 euros target price * Voestalpine <VOES.VI>: Barclays raises target to 40 eur from 39.50 eur; rating overweight